# Test Cases - Turbo Rush

This file contains manual test cases for the `Turbo Rush - Death Road` browser game, organized into smaller sections.

## Test Environment

- Browser: Chrome, Edge, or another modern browser
- Required files in the same folder:
  - `racing_game_v5.html`
  - `racing_game_v5.css`
  - `racing_game_v5.js`

## 1. Launch and Startup

| TC ID | Scenario | Steps | Expected Result |
|------|----------|-------|-----------------|
| TC-01 | Game file opens | Open `racing_game_v5.html` in a browser | Game loads successfully |
| TC-02 | Developer intro appears | Launch the game | Intro overlay is displayed |
| TC-03 | Developer credit is correct | Watch the intro screen | `Samay Chutani` appears in the credits |
| TC-04 | Name input appears | Wait for intro to finish | Name input overlay is shown |

## 2. Name Entry

| TC ID | Scenario | Steps | Expected Result |
|------|----------|-------|-----------------|
| TC-05 | Empty name is blocked | Press Enter without typing a name | User does not continue |
| TC-06 | Valid name is accepted | Enter a valid name and submit | Lobby screen opens |
| TC-07 | Enter key submits name | Type a name and press Enter | Name is accepted and lobby opens |

